        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/351/655/original/c9e40d0b-13c0-49a6-a133-cf3bd377fb1f.png" srcset="" alt="Open Calendar" height="612" width="96">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_73E80C50-1EDB-0135-7823-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Global Navigation, click the <strong>Calendar</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="add_assignment" data-step-uuid="644A4E1A-2154-4599-8A78-9EA1C911208F">
    <h2 id="add_assignment" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Assignment</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/772/979/original/ac8816ca-3bbb-4853-9cd6-9d22e8cf296a.png" srcset="" alt="Add Assignment" height="71" width="385">
